        <article class="clearfix">
            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <h4>Eugenics</h4><p>关键词：反乌托邦、黑色幽默</p><p>发售日期：6月28日</p><p>你是实验殖民地 UT-OP-I4的遗传负责人，居民的下一代基因由你来掌控。发掘并识别人类的种种基因，为了打造更美好的社会，而让更优秀的人诞生吧！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eugenics19046gV.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13938" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eugenics29052YY.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13939" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Eugenics39059uM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13940" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/935610/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>NOYO-!</h4><p>关键词：JRPG</p><p>发售日期：7月3日</p><p>大家都因为智能手机上的“DokuDenpa"而变得疯狂，幸好 Noyo 没有智能手机，她决定帮助大家恢复日常生活，带着两只猫踏上了冒险旅程。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-NOYO11350pp.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13941" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-NOYO21356vv.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13942" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-NOYO31362Ue.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13943" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1093300/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Total Party Kill</h4><p>关键词：平台解谜</p><p>发售日期：7月3日</p><p>LD43“必须做出牺牲”的作品。法师、战士、弓箭手组队探险地牢，但只有牺牲你的同伴才能够通向深处！战士可以将人扔出去，法师可以将人冻成冰块，弓箭手可以把人钉在墙上。合理地“使用”你的同伴，让至少一个英雄到达终点以通过关卡！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Total_Party_Kill1822QJ.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13944" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1091250/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Kubifaktorium</h4><p>关键词：模拟、城镇建造</p><p>发售日期：7月3日</p><p>建立殖民地，让居民收集资源、制造工具和武器，探索不同的生物群系。物流运输和自动化会是你城镇的关键建设部分，如何让城市生产更高效？尝试不断优化你的自动化方案！游戏支持 mod，暂无中文（不过 steam 页面有中文介绍，可能快了）。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Kubifaktorium2549Mc.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13945" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/898720/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Shadowland</h4><p>关键词：光影解谜</p><p>发售日期：7月4日</p><p>利用光源和阴影解谜，让主角到达终点。有时你也会摆脱这片灰蒙蒙的世界，从3D 夹层中操控机关。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Shadowland3151st.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13946" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1091180/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Atma</h4><p>关键词：冒险、动作</p><p>发售日期：7月4日</p><p>在人类与灵魂共处的世界中，你已过世的爱人向你求助。作为现实与精神世界平衡的守护者，你是否要背弃诺言，打破平衡将爱人带回现世呢？</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Atma337291C.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13950" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Atma23739hs.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13951" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Atma137498h.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13952" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1096590/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Traffix</h4><p>关键词：益智、解谜</p><p>发售日期：7月5日</p><p>交通永远是大城市的难题！手动控制你的红绿灯开关，以相对最好的方法保证整个交通系统正常运行。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Traffix13363m4.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13947" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Traffix23368gU.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13948" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Traffix33374O5.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13949" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1102580/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Combo Postage</h4><p>关键词：休闲、益智</p><p>发售日期：7月6日</p><p>为快递箱打包，一口气寄出去！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/07/pic-Combo_Postage4214d6.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13953" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/881470/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>其他值得关注的游戏</h4><ul><li>STG 佳作 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1067720/Hellsinker/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Hellsinker.</a></li><li>3D 像素画编辑器<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1106180/SpriteStack/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">SpriteStack</a>（绘制体素、像素渲染）</li><li>休闲平台跳跃游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1080630/Hero_Express/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Hero Express</a></li></ul>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>

